  "text": "A similar PO-based approach for FSS radomes was suggested for the first time in [CITATION_1] , where the equivalent current were computed on the basis of the simple GO approach over a uniform surface exhibiting the reflection coefficient of the FSS. In this paper, instead, equivalent currents are considered non-uniform and numerically computed via a full wave FE simulation.",
